{
    "title": "Kafka - Overview",
    "description": "This dashboard visualizes key Kafka metrics so you can monitor the flow of data through your infrastructure and spot potential issues like excessive leader changes. Also included are Zookeeper and JVM metrics to ensure your Kafka service has sufficient resources. For further reading on Kafka monitoring: \n\n- [Datadog's guide to monitoring Kafka performance](https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/monitoring-kafka-performance-metrics)\n\n- [How to collect Kafka performance metrics](https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/collecting-kafka-performance-metrics/)\n\n- [How to monitor Kafka with Datadog](https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/monitor-kafka-with-datadog/)- [Tools for scaling Kafka](https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/engineering/introducing-kafka-kit-tools-for-scaling-kafka/)\n\n- [Datadogâ€™s Kafka integration docs](https://docs.datadoghq.com/integrations/kafka/).\n\nClone this template dashboard to make changes and add your own graph widgets. ",
    "widgets": [
        {
            "id": 0,
            "definition": {
                "type": "timeseries",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "sum:kafka.consumer_lag{$consumer_group} by {host,consumer_group}",
                        "display_type": "line"
                    }
                ],
                "custom_links": [],
                "title": "Consumer lag by group",
                "title_size": "16",
                "title_align": "left",
                "time": {
                    "live_span": "4h"
                },
                "show_legend": false,
                "legend_size": "0"
            },
            "layout": {
                "x": 113,
                "y": 12,
                "width": 46,
                "height": 16
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 1,
            "definition": {
                "type": "query_value",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "sum:kafka.replication.under_replicated_partitions{*}",
                        "aggregator": "sum",
                        "conditional_formats": [
                            {
                                "comparator": "<=",
                                "value": 0,
                                "palette": "white_on_green"
                            },
                            {
                                "comparator": ">=",
                                "value": 10,
                                "palette": "white_on_red"
                            },
                            {
                                "comparator": ">=",
                                "value": 10,
                                "palette": "white_on_yellow"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ],
                "custom_links": [],
                "title": "Under replicated",
                "title_size": "16",
                "title_align": "center",
                "time": {
                    "live_span": "5m"
                },
                "precision": 0
            },
            "layout": {
                "x": 0,
                "y": 29,
                "width": 15,
                "height": 16
            }
        },
        {
